**LIX Calculator:** https://www.skolverket.se/undervisning/stod-i-undervisningen/sprak-och-kunskapsutveckling/stod-i-undervisningen-for-digital-kompetens/textbearbetning-och-undervisning/lix-lasbarhetsindex

**Method:**

* Number of words: 62
* Number of long words (over 6 letters): 16
* Number of sentences: 7
* Average sentence length (words/sentence): 8.86
* Percentage of long words: 16/62 * 100 = 25.81%

**Formula:**

```
LIX = ((Ordlängd * Procentsats långa ord) / Meningslängd) * 100
```

**Calculation:**

```
LIX = ((8.86 * 25.81) / 8.86) * 100 = 28.91
```

**Result:**

LIX = 28.91